page.title: 20BIOGRAPHY OF WENHAM
page.content: Sir Leslie Boreham,High Court Judge and Lady Boreham reside at Wenham Hill. During his early years at Wenham Hill he planted a grove of larch trees for his grandchildren, some of whom live at Manor House Great Wenham and others at Capel St.Mary. Dr.Michael Bush Community Health Physician for Suffolk resides at Cherry Place. Contributors to this project are as follows:Mrs.G.M.Samways,Mrs Mitzi Tyler Mrs. Crisp,Mrs Jane Clark,Mrs Matthews, G.R.Horrex Mr.Pollock Mrs.Kathy Pollard, Mrs.S.Thomas.,
